    "title": {
      "rendered": "6 Fresh Ideas for Your Nonprofit&#8217;s &#8220;Thank You&#8221; Landing Page"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Thank-You-Landing-Page-Square.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-16443\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Thank You Landing Page Square\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Thank-You-Landing-Page-Square-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Thank-You-Landing-Page-Square.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Thank-You-Landing-Page-Square.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Thank-You-Landing-Page-Square.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Thank-You-Landing-Page-Square.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Thank-You-Landing-Page-Square.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Each time <strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/nonprofitorgs\">@NonprofitOrgs</a></strong> reaches a 100K-follower benchmark, Nonprofit Tech for Good donates to various nonprofits. It&#8217;s a way to give back, but its also a system used to periodically\u00a0review how nonprofits are innovating their online giving process. In this last round of donations &#8211; $25 to 28 nonprofits ($700 for reaching 700K followers), some progress has been made since the last round of donations made at 600K followers. More nonprofits are streamlining their online giving process and using more visuals to communicate their gratitude to donors.</p>\n<p>A &#8220;Thank You&#8221; landing page is the page that donors land on after their donation has been made. It&#8217;s an important page because it is one of the few times you have the hyperfocused attention of your donors as they wait for their credit card payment to be processed and confirmed. Yet surprisingly it is one of the most overlooked web pages on a nonprofit&#8217;s website. Most &#8220;Thank You&#8221; landing pages appear as though they haven&#8217;t been updated since the early 2000&#8217;s, but as many nonprofit have launched new responsively designed websites since the last round of donations, &#8220;Thank You&#8221; landing pages are slowly but surely getting redesigned to accommodate today&#8217;s mobile and social donors.</p>\n<p><strong>Important:</strong> It was shocking\u00a0how many nonprofits I wanted to donate to, but couldn&#8217;t because of bugs in their donation process. Ten out of 38 nonprofits had bugs in their donation process that prohibited donations from be successfully completed. That&#8217;s a 26% failure rate!\u00a0PayPal was the worst. Five of the ten nonprofits that I wanted to donate to\u00a0did not receive donations because of a PayPal bug.\u00a0<em>If your nonprofit has not donated to itself in the last few months, I highly recommend you do so immediately and then commit to doing so at least once monthly to both discover bugs and always have in the forefront of your mind the donor experience and how it can be improved.</em></p>\n<h2>1. Prominently feature a &#8220;Thank You&#8221; video.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.oxfamamerica.org/donate/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16423\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Oxfam Landing Page 2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Oxfam-Landing-Page-2.png?resize=600%2C280\" width=\"600\" height=\"280\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Oxfam-Landing-Page-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Oxfam-Landing-Page-2.png?resize=300%2C140&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong><a href=\"http://www.oxfamamerica.org/donate/\">Donate: Oxfam America</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">2. Add a poll asking donors what prompted them to give.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://support.worldwildlife.org/site/SPageServer?pagename=main_monthly_donation_2014&amp;s_src=AWG1412SS9B2\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16424\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"WWF Thank You Landing Page 2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/WWF-Thank-You-Landing-Page-2.png?resize=600%2C334\" width=\"600\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/WWF-Thank-You-Landing-Page-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/WWF-Thank-You-Landing-Page-2.png?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong><a href=\"https://support.worldwildlife.org/site/SPageServer?pagename=main_monthly_donation_2014&amp;s_src=AWG1412SS9B2\">Donate: World Wildlife Fund</a></strong></p>\n<h2>3. Use images to bring attention to calls-to-action.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://support.worldwildlife.org/site/SPageServer?pagename=main_monthly_donation_2014&amp;s_src=AWG1412SS9B2\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16427\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"WWF Thank You Landing Page 3\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/WWF-Thank-You-Landing-Page-3.png?resize=600%2C335\" width=\"600\" height=\"335\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/WWF-Thank-You-Landing-Page-3.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/WWF-Thank-You-Landing-Page-3.png?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><strong></strong></a><strong><a href=\"https://support.worldwildlife.org/site/SPageServer?pagename=main_monthly_donation_2014&amp;s_src=AWG1412SS9B2\">Donate: World Wildlife Fund</a></strong></p>\n<h2>4. Add large, colorful social network icons.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://support.worldwildlife.org/site/SPageServer?pagename=main_monthly_donation_2014&amp;s_src=AWG1412SS9B2\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16426\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"WWF Thank You Landing Page 4\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/WWF-Thank-You-Landing-Page-4.png?resize=600%2C227\" width=\"600\" height=\"227\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/WWF-Thank-You-Landing-Page-4.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/WWF-Thank-You-Landing-Page-4.png?resize=300%2C113&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><strong></strong></a><strong><a href=\"https://support.worldwildlife.org/site/SPageServer?pagename=main_monthly_donation_2014&amp;s_src=AWG1412SS9B2\">Donate: World Wildlife Fund</a></strong></p>\n<h2>5. Enable donors to share their donation with their social networks.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://secure2.convio.net/cintl/site/Donation2?df_id=10263&amp;10263.donation=form1&amp;__utma=221478794.44579794.1404403274.1404405154.1404565072.3&amp;__utmb=221478794.2.9.1404565074113&amp;__utmc=221478794&amp;__utmx=-&amp;__utmz=221478794.1404403274.1.1.utmcsr=(direct)%7Cutmccn=(direct)%7Cutmcmd=(none)&amp;__utmv=-&amp;__utmk=15202869\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-16429\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Conservation International Thank You Landing Page\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Conservation-International-Thank-You-Landing-Page.png?resize=600%2C425\" width=\"600\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Conservation-International-Thank-You-Landing-Page.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Conservation-International-Thank-You-Landing-Page.png?resize=300%2C212&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong><a href=\"https://secure2.convio.net/cintl/site/Donation2?df_id=10263&amp;10263.donation=form1&amp;__utma=221478794.44579794.1404403274.1404405154.1404565072.3&amp;__utmb=221478794.2.9.1404565074113&amp;__utmc=221478794&amp;__utmx=-&amp;__utmz=221478794.1404403274.1.1.utmcsr=(direct)%7Cutmccn=(direct)%7Cutmcmd=(none)&amp;__utmv=-&amp;__utmk=15202869\">Donate: Conservation International</a></strong></p>\n<h2>6. Allow donors to designate their just made donation as a tribute/honor gift.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.heifer.org/gift-catalog/give-where-needed-most-donation.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16431\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Heifer Thank You Landing Page2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Heifer-Thank-You-Landing-Page2.png?resize=600%2C494\" width=\"600\" height=\"494\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Heifer-Thank-You-Landing-Page2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Heifer-Thank-You-Landing-Page2.png?resize=300%2C247&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><strong><a href=\"http://www.heifer.org/gift-catalog/give-where-needed-most-donation.html\">Donate: Heifer International</a></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.<br />\n<strong> </strong></p>\n",
